snippet.title: Dragon Ball Z (Arcade) Playthrough longplay retro video game
snippet.description: Dragon Ball Z (ドラゴンボールZ, Doragon Bōru Zetto) is a video game for arcades based on the Dragon Ball Z series. It was designed and manufactured exclusively in Japan by Banpresto in 1993.
